2002-0278 (La. 10/25/02)

STATE of Louisiana v. Joseph MILLS. No. 2002-K-0278. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 25, 2002.

In re State of Louisiana; — Plaintiff; Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review, Parish of Orleans, Criminal District Court Div. F, No. 404-531; to the Court of Appeal, Fourth Circuit, No. 2000-KA-2525.

Denied.

TRAYLOR, J., would grant the writ. KNOLL, J., would grant the writ. WEIMER, J., would grant the writ.
